@startuml Keycloak Token State Machine
[*] --> Unverified : Token received in Header

Unverified --> KeyLookUp : Extract kid
KeyLookUp --> SignatureVerification : Public key resolved (Cache hit/fetch)
KeyLookUp --> AuthFailed : kid not matching / JWKS fetch error

SignatureVerification --> ClaimsVerification : Signature matches key
SignatureVerification --> AuthFailed : Signature mismatch / Invalid key

ClaimsVerification --> RoleVerification : Token not expired & tenant extracted
ClaimsVerification --> AuthFailed : Token expired / invalid claims format

RoleVerification --> Authenticated : User has matching role for resource
RoleVerification --> AuthForbidden : User lacks required role

Authenticated --> [*] : Security Context Propagated
AuthFailed --> [*] : 401 Unauthorized Returned
AuthForbidden --> [*] : 403 Forbidden Returned
@enduml
